<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Account Owner Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fc;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #222;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #4a90e2;
        background: #eaf3ff;
        padding: 10px 22px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid #4a90e2;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 12px 0;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      hr {
        border: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #ddd;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 18px;
        font-style: italic;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Verify Account Ownership</h1>
      <p>Hello, <strong>{{full_name}}</strong>!</p>
      <p>To proceed with a sensitive action on your account, we need to verify
        that you are the account owner.</p>
      <p>Your verification code is:</p>
      <div class='otp'>{{otp}}</div>
      <p>Please enter this code to confirm your identity and continue.</p>
      <p class='note'><strong>Note:</strong>
        This OTP is valid for 10 minutes.</p>
      <hr />
      <p class='footer'>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>